description: A wreath-laying service and address by the Bailiff will be streamed online, amongst other events.
title: Coronavirus: Guernsey's 'virtual' Liberation Day plans announced
title_page: Coronavirus: Guernsey's 'virtual' Liberation Day plans announced - BBC News
maintext: Deputy Matt Fallaize, president of the Committee for Education, Sport and Culture, said: "We have worked together with many amazing people, including the Guernsey Music Service, who are providing the virtual choir recordings of the hymns and the National Anthem for the church service.
